What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Smart Dishwasher Market?

Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Smart Dishwasher Market

Smart dishwasher market size is expected to grow at a compound annual rate of 10.1% in the forecast period 2021 to 2028 and is likely to reach USD 7,557.2 million by 2028. Data Bridge Market Research report on smart dishwasher market provides analysis and insights regarding the various factors expected to be prevalent throughout the forecasted period while providing their impacts on the market’s growth.

The smart dishwashers market refers to the sales of smart dishwashers and the services associated with it. It is used in commercial and household and has beneficial features such as Wi-Fi access, flexibility to use from smartphone, control through virtual assistant or voice control, can even clean utensils in very less time, has flexibility to address the collection of food waste and redepositing food particles.

The expansion in the commercial market especially the hotels, cafes, and restaurants where smart dishwashers are highly adopted and growing penetration of internet and smartphone and connected devices are expected to proliferate the overall demand for smart dishwasher market over the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Moreover, changing lifestyles, consumer preference for smart kitchen appliances and increased demand for home refurbishing with smart accessories and kitchenware due to its benefits such as effective and easy dishes cleaning, low requirement of manual activities and most importantly less water usage which are significant factors for the heightening demand of market. In addition to this, the smart dishwashers are highly flexible and efficient as they are integrated with features such as smartphone controls, virtual home assistant and Wi-Fi connectivity which accelerates demand for the market. However, the fluctuating prices of raw materials and high repairing and shipping costs is projected to impede the growth of the market.

The new product launch is anticipated to further generate new opportunities for the smart dishwasher market in the forecast period. The slowdown in production due to prevalence of COVID-19 across the globe is projected to be challenging for the growth of the market.

